ores de Saúde Integrados com EHR | Monitoramento Remoto e Engajamento do Paciente\",\"description\":\"Rastreie mais de 70 métricas de saúde, desde sinais vitais até estilo de vida. Dados de pacientes, provedores, dispositivos, Apple Health e Google Health Connect fluem para o EHR — impulsionando o Monitoramento Remoto de Pacientes, consultas e documentação assistida por AI.\",\"keywords\":\"rastreadores de saúde,monitoramento de saúde EHR,dados de saúde do paciente,dispositivos conectados,rastreamento de métricas de saúde,monitoramento remoto de pacientes,integração de assistente AI,gerenciamento de dados de saúde\"},\"structured_data\":{\"faq_page\":{\"questions\":[{\"question\":\"What are Health Trackers in the Virtual Practice?\",\"answer\":\"Health Trackers are a library of 70+ parameters—covering vitals, labs and lifestyle—that patients and providers can record. All data is stored in the patient's electronic health record (EHR).\"},{\"question\":\"How do Health Trackers improve care for providers?\",\"answer\":\"They provide a continuous view of patient health between visits, power Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM) care plans, and surface longitudinal trends during consultations.\"},{\"question\":\"Can patients log their own health data?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Patients can log readings in the portal or mobile app, and also sync data from compatible devices and health apps.\"},{\"question\":\"Which devices and health apps are supported?\",\"answer\":\"Health Trackers connect with Bluetooth-enabled monitors, wearables, and popular platforms like Apple Health (iOS) and Google Health Connect (Android).\"},{\"question\":\"Can providers add measurements during visits?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Providers can add vitals and other measurements during in-person or telehealth consultations so the EHR stays current.\"},{\"question\":\"How do Health Trackers support Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM)?\",\"answer\":\"Tracker data forms the foundation of RPM care plans. Teams can set personalized thresholds, assign monitoring roles, and receive alerts when values fall outside configured ranges.\"},{\"question\":\"Are patients actively involved with Health Trackers?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Patients can see their data, track goals, and collaborate with providers through shared monitoring and feedback.\"},{\"question\":\"Do Health Trackers integrate with AI features?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Tracker data in the EHR provides context for AI Scribe, helping generate richer, more accurate clinical notes.\"},{\"question\":\"Can clinics customize which trackers are available?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Admins can enable the subset of the 70+ trackers that fits their practice and tailor availability at the patient level.\"},{\"question\":\"Is tracker data secure and compliant?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. All tracker entries are stored securely within the patient's EHR under strict privacy and security controls across web and mobile.\"}]},\"software_application\":{\"name\":\"Health Trackers\",\"alternate_name\":\"EHR Health Trackers\",\"url\":\"https://www.continuouscare.io/health-trackers\",\"description\":\"Track 70+ patient health metrics—vitals, labs, and lifestyle—via manual entry, Bluetooth devices, and health platforms. All data is stored in the patient EHR and powers Remote Patient Monitoring care plans, consultations, trends, and AI-assisted documentation.\",\"features\":[\"70+ configurable health trackers (vitals, labs, lifestyle)\",\"Data entry by patients and providers\",\"Bluetooth device and wearable syncing\",\"Apple Health (iOS) and Google Health Connect (Android) integrations\",\"Trends and longitudinal charts in the EHR\",\"Foundation for RPM care plans (thresholds and alerts)\",\"Consultation-ready context for providers\",\"Context for AI Scribe clinical documentation\"],\"brand_name\":\"ContinuousCare\",\"brand_url\":\"https://www.continuouscare.io\",\"part_of_name\":\"Virtual Practice\",\"part_of_url\":\"https://www.continuouscare.io/virtual-practice\"}},\"hero\":{\"title_prefix\":\"Comprehensive\",\"title_highlight\":\"Health Tracking\",\"title_suffix\":\"for Better Patient Outcomes\",\"subtitle\":\"Empower patients to monitor their health metrics while providing healthcare providers with comprehensive, real-time data for informed care decisions.\",\"benefits\":[\"Multi-device health data integration\",\"Real-time vital signs monitoring\",\"Customizable health goal tracking\",\"Provider dashboard with alerts\"]},\"image_alts\":{\"hero\":\"Healthcare professional monitoring patient health data\",\"comprehensive_monitoring\":\"Comprehensive health monitoring dashboard\",\"clinical_integration\":\"Health trackers integrated into everyday clinical care\",\"device_compatibility\":\"Various health monitoring devices and wearables\",\"specialty_optimization\":\"Medical specialists using specialized monitoring tools\",\"patient_collaboration\":\"Healthcare provider and patient collaborating on health monitoring\"},\"supporting_strip\":{\"vital_signs\":\"Vital Signs\",\"health_conditions\":\"Health Conditions\",\"fitness_wellness\":\"Fitness \u0026 Wellness\",\"blood_tests\":\"Blood Tests\"},\"why_it_matters\":{\"title\":\"Why It Matters\",\"features\":[{\"title\":\"All in the EHR\",\"description\":\"Every tracker entry is stored in the patient's record — no silos.\"},{\"title\":\"Connect Devices \u0026 Apps\",\"description\":\"Patients sync from Apple Health, Google Health Connect, or devices.\"},{\"title\":\"Power RPM Care Plans\",\"description\":\"Tracker data fuels personalized thresholds, alerts, and monitoring.\"},{\"title\":\"Smarter Documentation\",\"description\":\"AI Scribe uses tracker data to generate richer, context-aware notes.\"}]},\"comprehensive_coverage\":{\"badge\":\"Comprehensive Parameter Coverage\",\"title\":\"Complete Health Monitoring\",\"subtitle\":\"Track 70+ health metrics — from vitals to lifestyle — all unified in the patient's EHR, with data flowing in from patients, providers, and devices to support continuous care.\",\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Vital Signs \u0026 Physiological Data\",\"description\":\"Monitor blood pressure, heart rate, SpO₂, weight, temperature, and more with real-time syncing from devices or manual entry.\"},{\"title\":\"Chronic Condition Parameters\",\"description\":\"Track glucose, respiratory rate, and other markers critical for managing diabetes, hypertension, COPD, and cardiac conditions.\"},{\"title\":\"Fitness \u0026 Wellness Metrics\",\"description\":\"Follow activity, sleep, body composition, menstrual cycles, nutrition, and mood to support preventive and holistic care.\"},{\"title\":\"Specialty-Specific Indicators\",\"description\":\"Enable the right subset of trackers for each specialty — from kidney and liver function to women's health — tailored to patient needs.\"}]},\"everyday_care\":{\"badge\":\"Everyday Care Integration\",\"title\":\"Health Trackers in Everyday Care\",\"subtitle\":\"Health Trackers are more than data points — they form the backbone of continuous care inside the Virtual Practice. From powering Remote Patient Monitoring plans to supporting providers during consultations, they ensure patient health information is always actionable.\",\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Foundation for RPM\",\"description\":\"Personalized thresholds and alerts in Remote Patient Monitoring plans are built directly on tracker data.\"},{\"title\":\"Consultation Context\",\"description\":\"Providers can review longitudinal health trends during encounters, add new measurements, and use the information to guide treatment decisions.\"},{\"title\":\"Team-Based Monitoring\",\"description\":\"Assign monitoring responsibilities to a team of providers so patient data never goes unnoticed.\"},{\"title\":\"Smarter Documentation\",\"description\":\"Tracker data is stored in the EHR and referenced by tools like AI Scribe, helping providers create accurate, context-rich notes.\"}]},\"device_connectivity\":{\"badge\":\"Device Connectivity\",\"title\":\"Extens