red Health Notes \u0026 Sharing\",\"page_description\":\"Discover the Health Journal feature in Virtual Practice. A secure digital space for patients to log health notes, reflections, and symptoms. Patients control what to share, while providers can add comments for better collaboration in care.\",\"product_name\":\"Virtual Practice – Health Journal\",\"product_description\":\"The Health Journal is part of the Virtual Practice Electronic Health Record. It provides patients with a secure space to write health notes, reflections, or symptoms, and share selected entries with their healthcare providers. Providers can also add comments to shared entries, improving collaboration and continuity of care.\",\"features\":[\"Secure digital journaling\",\"Patient-controlled sharing of entries\",\"Provider comments on shared notes\",\"Accessible via patient portal and mobile app\",\"Integrated with patient health record\"]},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Personal Health\",\"title_highlight\":\"Journaling\",\"title_suffix\":\"Made Simple\",\"subtitle\":\"Give patients a secure space to record their health journey and, when they choose, share valuable insights with their care team.\",\"benefits\":[\"Secure digital journaling\",\"Patient-controlled sharing\",\"Integrated with the health record\",\"Accessible on web and mobile\"],\"image_alt\":\"Patient documenting health journey in digital journal\"},\"problem_section\":{\"title\":\"Why a Health Journal Matters in Everyday Care\",\"subtitle\":\"Healthcare conversations are short, but health changes happen every day. The Health Journal helps bridge this gap.\",\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Capture daily experiences\",\"description\":\"Patients can note symptoms, progress, or reflections between visits.\"},{\"title\":\"Support recall\",\"description\":\"Journals help patients remember what happened since their last appointment.\"},{\"title\":\"Provide context\",\"description\":\"Providers see a richer picture when patients choose to share.\"},{\